# Docs Template Enforcement

**MANDATORY for all docs/ writes/updates**:

1. **Single Entry**: Always start at [docs/Home.md](docs/Home.md) (MOC with [[wikilinks]] only).
2. **Template**: Use [docs/templates/Recycler-Note-Template.md](docs/templates/Recycler-Note-Template.md) exactly:
   - YAML frontmatter: title, tags [obsidian, recycle-ai, <topic>], aliases (MOC if applicable), status, published, created/updated.
   - Sections: # Title, ## Overview, ## Purpose, ## Key Concepts, ## Implementation Details, ## Related Topics ([[wikilinks]]), ## For Agents, ## Backlinks.
3. **Size**: 50-200 lines; group related content (e.g., schema+reducers in one MD); split large topics.
4. **Obsidian**: [[wikilinks]] only (no [markdown](paths)), mermaid for flows, bidirectional links for graph.
5. **LLM**: Concise bullets/code, no fluff/repetition, "For Agents" section with navigation/token tips.

Violation: Rewrite to template. Update Home.md MOC if new note.